531
00:38:13,101 --> 00:38:14,484
Park Soo Ha?

532
00:38:14,535 --> 00:38:16,739
His name is Park Soo Ha? Not Kim Joong Ki.

533
00:38:16,739 --> 00:38:18,892
No, it's not.

534
00:38:19,999 --> 00:38:21,943
I'm Kim Joong Ki.

535
00:38:21,970 --> 00:38:24,271
