536
00:38:24,345 --> 00:38:26,177
Ah, no...

537
00:38:31,100 --> 00:38:32,972
His name is Park Soo Ha?

538
00:38:36,253 --> 00:38:37,626
<i> Do you remember me? </i>

539
00:38:37,626 --> 00:38:39,708
<i>Because you seem familiar.</i>

540
00:38:48,781 --> 00:38:50,431
Student.

541
00:38:50,431 --> 00:38:53,192
Do you happen to know Park Soo Ha's phone number?

542
00:38:53,700 --> 00:38:55,909
- Cheers!
- Cheers!

543
00:39:03,689 --> 00:39:05,615
Lawyer Jang, why don't you have a glass of wine too?

