00:39:17,073 --> 00:39:19,038
Is something on my face?

549
00:39:19,122 --> 00:39:20,985
No,

550
00:39:20,985 --> 00:39:23,049
you're inviting me to dinner parties,

551
00:39:23,049 --> 00:39:24,742
