552
00:39:24,742 --> 00:39:26,301
It's weird.

553
00:39:26,330 --> 00:39:27,786
You weren't like this before.

554
00:39:27,786 --> 00:39:28,921
Usually,

555
00:39:28,921 --> 00:39:31,194
I'm a bit harsh on people without talent.

556
00:39:31,224 --> 00:39:35,112
Eh, so you're saying Lawyer Jang didn't have talent?

557
00:39:35,112 --> 00:39:36,768
Of course she didn't.

558
00:39:36,768 --> 00:39:38,614
But with Lawyer Cha, you dropped honorifics right away.

559
00:39:38,614 --> 00:39:41,057
He's a talented guy.

560
00:39:41,057 --> 00:39:43,901
You saw his trial just a while ago too.

561
00:39:43,954 --> 00:39:45,691
Eh, Lawyer Shin.

562
00:39:46,774 --> 00:39:48,516
Did you call me to the dinner for this?

563
00:39:48,516 --> 00:39:49,832
To compare in each other's presence?

564
00:39:49,849 --> 00:39:52,012
